@fiannafailparty @BusConnects @HolyChildCS @SCFEOfficial @GraduateDublin Secondly, #BusConnects are proposing to retain the direct route (No. 7) from Loughlinstown Park to the City Centre (calling it the 98). This is a significant change and really welcome. But the hourly frequency is insufficient, so there's more work to be done. https://t.co/m3lAFpkArb
